1
00:01:32,539 --> 00:01:36,720
[Eternal Brotherhood 2]

2
00:01:41,320 --> 00:01:44,830
[Episode 23]

3
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:49,350
Your Highness,

4
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:51,070
according to the customs
of the North Clan,

5
00:01:51,070 --> 00:01:52,789
before the birth of a royal heir,

6
00:01:52,789 --> 00:01:54,780
one must visit the Holy Wall Altar

7
00:01:54,950 --> 00:01:58,680
to pray for blessings upon
both the North Clan and the royal family,

8
00:01:58,759 --> 00:02:00,840
and pray that the barbarians
from the Eastern Wilderness

9
00:02:00,840 --> 00:02:02,510
do not cross the Holy Wall.

10
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:05,920
The Divine Emperor has had
no grandchildren before,

11
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:08,650
so Your Highness's journey
is of great significance.

12
00:02:08,650 --> 00:02:10,250
I implore you to be cautious.

13
00:02:12,660 --> 00:02:14,750
Thank you for the reminder,
Counsellor Black Veil.

14
00:02:14,750 --> 00:02:16,630
The journey will be bumpy.

15
00:02:17,430 --> 00:02:18,630
General-in-Chief,

16
00:02:18,960 --> 00:02:20,310
you must not let my daughter

17
00:02:20,310 --> 00:02:22,110
suffer even the slightest harm.

18
00:02:22,560 --> 00:02:24,690
I, Yun Qianxue, will not fail in my duty

19
00:02:24,930 --> 00:02:26,270
to protect the Princess.

20
00:02:26,270 --> 00:02:27,340
I should've

21
00:02:27,710 --> 00:02:29,750
gone with you on this pilgrimage.

22
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:32,050
But unfortunately,
state affairs are pressing.

23
00:02:32,050 --> 00:02:33,940
I know you dote on me,

24
00:02:35,150 --> 00:02:37,579
but I am the daughter
of the Divine Emperor of Sairong.

25
00:02:37,579 --> 00:02:40,320
How can I always remain
sheltered under your wing?

26
00:02:40,320 --> 00:02:43,090
Rest assured,
I will take good care of myself.

27
00:02:43,310 --> 00:02:44,079
Good.

28
00:02:52,560 --> 00:02:54,220
Take good care of my daughter.

29
00:02:54,710 --> 00:02:55,770
Yes, Your Majesty.

30
00:03:05,710 --> 00:03:07,560
Father kept reminding you,

31
00:03:08,330 --> 00:03:12,170
but we both know this trip
was never meant to go as planned.

32
00:03:14,770 --> 00:03:17,170
Your Highness, your delivery is imminent.

33
00:03:17,440 --> 00:03:20,150
If you want to stay out of sight
of everyone in Sairong City,

34
00:03:20,150 --> 00:03:23,030
praying at the Holy Wall
is the only opportunity.

35
00:03:25,910 --> 00:03:27,150
But when we return,

36
00:03:27,400 --> 00:03:29,020
Father will surely not let you off easily.

37
00:03:29,020 --> 00:03:32,280
Everything is for
Your Highness's reputation and safety.

38
00:03:32,920 --> 00:03:35,430
Your Highness,
you don't need to worry about it anymore.

39
00:03:35,430 --> 00:03:36,310
Let's depart.

40
00:03:44,950 --> 00:03:47,079
My Lord, the Governor of Liuyang District

41
00:03:47,079 --> 00:03:48,280
didn't attend the banquet.

42
00:03:48,280 --> 00:03:50,500
It doesn't necessarily mean
he's against us.

43
00:03:50,500 --> 00:03:52,910
Perhaps he's just out of the loop.

44
00:03:53,520 --> 00:03:56,320
That's why we're paying
a personal visit this time

45
00:03:56,360 --> 00:03:58,120
to discuss the future plans
for Yuanzhou together.

46
00:03:58,120 --> 00:03:59,579
Though Lu Di was defeated,

47
00:03:59,800 --> 00:04:01,400
the North Clan's strength in Yuanzhou now

48
00:04:01,400 --> 00:04:02,520
cannot be underestimated.

49
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:04,240
Many districts are still afraid of
the North Clan.

50
00:04:04,240 --> 00:04:06,120
Liuyang District is still
sitting on the fence now.

51
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:08,320
We need to find a way to solve this issue.

52
00:04:08,590 --> 00:04:10,390
It's not as serious as you think.

53
00:04:10,470 --> 00:04:12,470
In fact, most districts in Yuanzhou

54
00:04:12,630 --> 00:04:14,680
still want to break free
from the North Clan's control.

55
00:04:14,680 --> 00:04:15,470
This time,

56
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:17,560
we'll treat it as a friendly visit.

57
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:20,019
Just be careful and cautious
in our actions.

58
00:04:21,390 --> 00:04:22,190
Governor,

59
00:04:23,750 --> 00:04:25,120
Jialai District

60
00:04:25,120 --> 00:04:27,320
and he are now under your control.

61
00:04:28,170 --> 00:04:31,050
I will not disappoint
the King of Light's trust.

62
00:04:34,640 --> 00:04:35,900
Ladies and gentlemen,

63
00:04:36,540 --> 00:04:38,340
once we arrive in Liuyang,

64
00:04:38,760 --> 00:04:40,890
you all set up camp nearby.

65
00:04:41,230 --> 00:04:44,090
I'll take a few people
to scout the situation first.

66
00:04:44,360 --> 00:04:45,220
Understood!

67
00:04:47,300 --> 00:04:51,050
[Holy Wall Altar]

68
00:05:00,270 --> 00:05:03,980
Legend has it that the Holy Wall was built

69
00:05:05,270 --> 00:05:09,070
over several generations by
North Clan leaders a thousand years ago.

70
00:05:09,070 --> 00:05:10,250
How much blood and life

71
00:05:10,250 --> 00:05:12,740
they sacrificed for this

72
00:05:14,320 --> 00:05:15,480
is unknown.

73
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:17,520
But the vicissitudes of history

74
00:05:17,830 --> 00:05:19,830
are all carved on these stone walls.

75
00:05:20,680 --> 00:05:22,480
How the former North Clan people

76
00:05:23,090 --> 00:05:24,680
managed to create

77
00:05:25,130 --> 00:05:26,790
such a magnificent structure

78
00:05:27,950 --> 00:05:29,080
is truly admirable.

79
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:33,830
That's why it's called a wonder.

80
00:05:35,520 --> 00:05:37,320
Heaven will bless Your Highness

81
00:05:37,830 --> 00:05:39,360
and protect our North Clan.

82
00:05:40,750 --> 00:05:41,480
However...

83
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:44,950
It's about time.

84
00:05:47,890 --> 00:05:48,690
You mean...

85
00:05:48,750 --> 00:05:51,600
It's about time.

86
00:05:51,620 --> 00:05:52,830
I'll help you inside right away.

87
00:05:52,830 --> 00:05:53,430
No.

88
00:05:53,710 --> 00:05:56,390
You are not of the royal bloodline
and cannot enter.

89
00:05:56,390 --> 00:05:58,070
The method of praying for blessings

90
00:05:58,070 --> 00:06:01,000
is passed down orally
only within our royal lineage.

91
00:06:01,240 --> 00:06:03,700
I absolutely cannot bring you
into the cave.

92
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:05,130
But I was planning to

93
00:06:05,390 --> 00:06:07,630
arrange the accident
after the blessing ceremony.

94
00:06:07,630 --> 00:06:08,720
Now, I can only...

95
00:06:08,720 --> 00:06:09,720
It's too late.

96
00:06:11,390 --> 00:06:13,510
Now, all I can do is stay calm,

97
00:06:13,960 --> 00:06:16,400
dismiss everyone, and enter the cave.

98
00:06:17,480 --> 00:06:21,160
You stay outside the cave and protect me.

99
00:06:23,150 --> 00:06:25,550
Lord Yun, you must follow my instructions.

100
00:06:33,270 --> 00:06:36,480
The blessing ceremony is about to begin.

101
00:06:41,159 --> 00:06:44,560
Respectfully seeing off Your Highness.

102
00:06:58,640 --> 00:07:00,500
The flower of the mountain forest

103
00:07:01,110 --> 00:07:03,510
is sheltered by the lush canopy,

104
00:07:04,400 --> 00:07:05,930
while the lotus in the water

105
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:08,430
is guarded by drifting plankton
and scattered gravel.

106
00:07:08,430 --> 00:07:10,270
I, Ka Dan, have arrived safely.

107
00:07:11,360 --> 00:07:13,090
Thank you all for your efforts.

108
00:07:14,790 --> 00:07:16,390
As I go to pray for blessings,

109
00:07:16,390 --> 00:07:22,000
I will surely pray for
the longevity and peace of the North Clan.

110
00:10:29,550 --> 00:10:30,550
Your Highness...

111
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:43,860
Your Highness!

112
00:10:44,590 --> 00:10:47,250
Guards, escort the Princess
back to the palace!

113
00:10:48,750 --> 00:10:50,030
Divine Emperor above,

114
00:10:50,270 --> 00:10:52,600
I, Yun Qianxue, failed to
protect the Princess properly,

115
00:10:52,600 --> 00:10:55,310
causing the royal grandson
to be born at the Holy Wall Altar

116
00:10:55,310 --> 00:10:57,240
and resulting in
the Princess's premature labor.

117
00:10:57,240 --> 00:10:59,110
I deserve death for this crime.

118
00:11:54,000 --> 00:11:54,960
Rise.

119
00:11:56,320 --> 00:12:00,250
The accompanying personnel
have already given me a detailed account.

120
00:12:00,790 --> 00:12:04,840
Who could have
prevented a premature birth?

121
00:12:06,750 --> 00:12:10,280
Perhaps this is simply the will of heaven.

122
00:12:10,630 --> 00:12:13,020
Regardless, my crime is unforgivable.

123
00:12:13,670 --> 00:12:15,400
You are my daughter's husband,

124
00:12:15,890 --> 00:12:18,550
and now you're
the father of the royal grandson.

125
00:12:19,040 --> 00:12:20,630
Do you expect me to kill you?

126
00:12:22,150 --> 00:12:22,870
Stand up!

127
00:12:25,960 --> 00:12:29,840
There are more important matters
to attend to now.

128
00:12:31,120 --> 00:12:33,550
Someone has betrayed the North Clan.

129
00:12:35,930 --> 00:12:39,020
Read out Ling Buxu's letter.

130
00:12:43,550 --> 00:12:45,680
Under the siege of rebels in Yuanzhou,

131
00:12:45,680 --> 00:12:47,680
Lu Di suffered defeat after defeat,

132
00:12:47,910 --> 00:12:49,600
deliberately concealing
the state of the war

133
00:12:49,600 --> 00:12:52,480
and resulting in the loss
of over 20 districts in Yuanzhou.

134
00:12:52,480 --> 00:12:55,540
I request to dismiss Lu Di
and send support to Yuanzhou.

135
00:12:56,630 --> 00:12:57,690
As of now, Yuanzhou

136
00:12:59,210 --> 00:13:01,170
is no longer under our control.

137
00:13:01,610 --> 00:13:04,830
This is shocking and hard to accept.

138
00:13:06,450 --> 00:13:07,980
Even dying a thousand times

139
00:13:08,270 --> 00:13:11,550
wouldn't be enough to
atone for Lu Di's sins.

140
00:13:12,390 --> 00:13:14,240
What's even more ridiculous is that

141
00:13:14,240 --> 00:13:17,480
Ling Buxu sent several companies
of messengers,

142
00:13:20,480 --> 00:13:22,610
all of whom were assassinated by Lu Di.

143
00:13:22,680 --> 00:13:25,130
This one was a bit luckier

144
00:13:25,320 --> 00:13:26,850
and made it to Sairong City.

145
00:13:27,080 --> 00:13:28,080
Father,

146
00:13:28,910 --> 00:13:32,240
I suggest dispatching
law enforcement officers right away

147
00:13:32,550 --> 00:13:35,150
to Yuanzhou to execute Lu Di.

148
00:13:35,720 --> 00:13:39,770
General-in-Chief, what's your opinion?

149
00:13:45,600 --> 00:13:47,550
Prince Ka Lan once advised me

150
00:13:48,270 --> 00:13:51,750
that executing traitors
is crucial for establishing authority.

151
00:13:51,750 --> 00:13:52,790
Yes, Father.

152
00:13:53,280 --> 00:13:55,950
How to deal with the rebellion in Yuanzhou

153
00:13:56,440 --> 00:13:57,440
is the key point.

154
00:13:57,960 --> 00:13:59,290
If Your Majesty allows,

155
00:13:59,440 --> 00:14:01,270
I am willing to lead my troops

156
00:14:01,600 --> 00:14:03,910
to Yuanzhou to quell the rebellion.

157
00:14:04,150 --> 00:14:05,720
With just a command from Your Majesty,

158
00:14:05,720 --> 00:14:07,390
Lu Di's head will fall

159
00:14:08,030 --> 00:14:09,360
like it's nothing.

160
00:14:09,580 --> 00:14:13,410
Who do you two think is the most suitable

161
00:14:14,080 --> 00:14:16,230
to support Yuanzhou?

162
00:14:16,230 --> 00:14:18,960
Governor Luo Si of Jiana.

163
00:14:20,200 --> 00:14:23,000
Lord Luo Si is a renowned general
from our clan,

164
00:14:24,150 --> 00:14:26,480
with extensive battlefield experience.

165
00:14:26,840 --> 00:14:29,510
I believe sending him

166
00:14:31,440 --> 00:14:34,200
will surely defeat the rebels
in one stroke.

167
00:14:34,870 --> 00:14:40,110
Very well, it's decided then.

168
00:14:41,670 --> 00:14:44,840
Divine Emperor, our North Clan
is blessed by heaven.

169
00:14:45,520 --> 00:14:48,070
Yuanzhou will not be lost easily.

170
00:14:48,440 --> 00:14:51,120
Princess Ka Dan has offered prayers
for the blessings of the North Clan.

171
00:14:51,120 --> 00:14:53,360
Heaven will favor Sairong.

172
00:14:53,840 --> 00:14:56,370
I've been worried about
state affairs lately

173
00:14:58,000 --> 00:15:00,080
and almost forgot the main event.

174
00:15:04,920 --> 00:15:08,160
Princess Ka Dan has given birth to
a royal grandson.

175
00:15:08,870 --> 00:15:12,020
It's a day of national celebration.

176
00:15:19,550 --> 00:15:20,750
He's still sleeping?

177
00:15:27,070 --> 00:15:29,640
Look at the new little robe
I made for him.

178
00:15:29,670 --> 00:15:30,800
Isn't it beautiful?

179
00:15:30,840 --> 00:15:31,770
It's beautiful.

180
00:15:37,640 --> 00:15:40,790
I heard Lu Di lost Yuanzhou.

181
00:15:43,720 --> 00:15:45,720
I volunteered to support Yuanzhou.

182
00:15:46,320 --> 00:15:49,650
His Majesty didn't approve, instead...

183
00:15:49,870 --> 00:15:51,790
He sent Luo Si to Yuanzhou.

184
00:15:52,910 --> 00:15:55,970
Your Highness indeed understands
the Divine Emperor.

185
00:15:59,980 --> 00:16:02,340
Luo Si has always supported Ka Dun.

186
00:16:02,680 --> 00:16:05,560
It seems he wants to use
one force against another.

187
00:16:05,840 --> 00:16:07,000
The Divine Emperor

188
00:16:07,670 --> 00:16:10,600
has never liked Luo Si's attachment
to Prince Ka Dun.

189
00:16:10,870 --> 00:16:11,610
Moreover,

190
00:16:15,360 --> 00:16:17,390
the Data Tribe led by Luo Si

191
00:16:17,390 --> 00:16:20,050
has already posed a threat
to our Sairong Tribe.

192
00:16:20,630 --> 00:16:23,670
Weakening their strength
is the best strategy.

193
00:16:24,400 --> 00:16:25,730
The power to rule

194
00:16:25,760 --> 00:16:27,640
comes from both respect and fear.

195
00:16:28,670 --> 00:16:31,320
This incident will disgrace
the Sairong Tribe

196
00:16:31,320 --> 00:16:33,600
in the eyes of the entire North Clan.

197
00:16:34,030 --> 00:16:36,440
Luo Si will also look down on
our Sairong Tribe even more

198
00:16:36,440 --> 00:16:38,370
and might even wage war against us.

199
00:16:38,440 --> 00:16:41,370
Defeat the Sairong Tribe
and then command the world.

200
00:16:42,000 --> 00:16:43,000
The Sairong Tribe

201
00:16:43,550 --> 00:16:45,500
may appear to rule the North Clan,

202
00:16:45,600 --> 00:16:48,480
but we are also the ones

203
00:16:48,480 --> 00:16:50,140
everyone seeks to overthrow.

204
00:16:50,240 --> 00:16:52,240
The fear of being surpassed

205
00:16:52,240 --> 00:16:54,510
by other tribes

206
00:16:54,870 --> 00:16:57,000
lingers like a ghost,

207
00:16:57,390 --> 00:16:59,600
haunting Father's mind without end.

208
00:17:02,200 --> 00:17:03,550
And the ghost

209
00:17:05,440 --> 00:17:07,380
has never been this close.

210
00:17:12,200 --> 00:17:14,700
The King of Light, you have traveled
thousands of miles to come here,

211
00:17:14,700 --> 00:17:17,630
gracing Liuyang with your presence.

212
00:17:15,460 --> 00:17:19,099
[An Ge, Governor of Liuyang]

213
00:17:17,960 --> 00:17:20,310
Today, we must have a hearty drink.

214
00:17:20,589 --> 00:17:22,869
I didn't expect that
on this land of Yuanzhou,

215
00:17:22,869 --> 00:17:24,599
there would be such a paradise.

216
00:17:25,500 --> 00:17:26,910
I once heard a saying:

217
00:17:27,640 --> 00:17:32,000
"Raise the sticks and strike the drum,
ease the rhythm and sing in peace."

218
00:17:32,710 --> 00:17:34,240
The part about singing in peace

219
00:17:34,240 --> 00:17:37,720
must be referring to you.

220
00:17:40,160 --> 00:17:41,440
We Elves,

221
00:17:41,590 --> 00:17:43,110
value joy and freedom.

222
00:17:43,880 --> 00:17:46,400
Liuyang's land is fertile,

223
00:17:46,590 --> 00:17:48,680
so there are many engaged in farming.

224
00:17:48,680 --> 00:17:50,110
The people are simple and honest.

225
00:17:50,110 --> 00:17:53,960
Over the years in Yuanzhou,
we have always been non-competitive.

226
00:17:54,550 --> 00:17:57,550
Haven't you been disturbed
by the North Clan?

227
00:17:57,720 --> 00:18:00,240
If they come,
just let them take what they want.

228
00:18:00,240 --> 00:18:01,510
If given enough,

229
00:18:01,720 --> 00:18:03,110
trouble won't arise.

230
00:18:03,350 --> 00:18:05,830
Each Yuanzhou district has its own way

231
00:18:05,960 --> 00:18:07,360
of surviving to this day.

232
00:18:08,030 --> 00:18:09,560
It's not worth mentioning.

233
00:18:12,000 --> 00:18:14,130
The last time Jialai hosted a banquet,

234
00:18:14,240 --> 00:18:17,240
though I did not attend, I heard about it.

235
00:18:17,310 --> 00:18:20,480
It seems you are determined

236
00:18:20,500 --> 00:18:21,850
to unify Yuanzhou.

237
00:18:24,590 --> 00:18:26,880
Yuanzhou has been separated for too long,

238
00:18:26,880 --> 00:18:29,550
with each district shutting its doors
and relying on itself.

239
00:18:29,550 --> 00:18:31,110
Therefore, unifying Yuanzhou

240
00:18:31,110 --> 00:18:33,070
to prevent invasion by the North Clan

241
00:18:33,070 --> 00:18:35,070
is exactly why I have come.

242
00:18:35,400 --> 00:18:38,750
So, what do you plan to do?

243
00:18:40,310 --> 00:18:43,000
First, we must implement
a unified currency

244
00:18:43,350 --> 00:18:45,000
across all of Yuanzhou.

245
00:18:45,750 --> 00:18:48,030
This move has already gained support

246
00:18:48,030 --> 00:18:50,290
from most districts in Yuanzhou.

247
00:18:50,550 --> 00:18:52,030
A unified currency?

248
00:18:52,880 --> 00:18:54,510
For you, this move

249
00:18:55,160 --> 00:18:57,000
is all benefit and no harm.

250
00:19:01,310 --> 00:19:03,170
The King of Light, how about this?

251
00:19:03,550 --> 00:19:05,400
Let's have a drink first,

252
00:19:05,640 --> 00:19:08,640
and then continue our conversation,
shall we?

253
00:19:09,030 --> 00:19:09,510
Come on.

254
00:19:09,630 --> 00:19:10,360
Wait.

255
00:19:11,160 --> 00:19:13,290
Let me finish my last sentence first.

256
00:19:13,590 --> 00:19:15,020
Then I'll drink with you.

257
00:19:19,130 --> 00:19:22,180
Liuyang District is prosperous,

258
00:19:22,430 --> 00:19:24,290
and Governor An Ge is hospitable.

259
00:19:25,350 --> 00:19:26,240
Here,

260
00:19:26,650 --> 00:19:28,680
I send my blessings to them

261
00:19:29,090 --> 00:19:31,020
on behalf of others from Yuanzhou.

262
00:19:31,110 --> 00:19:31,590
Cheers!

263
00:19:40,990 --> 00:19:42,990
I am not good with alcohol.

264
00:19:43,510 --> 00:19:45,370
I'm known as a total lightweight.

265
00:19:45,590 --> 00:19:46,160
Do you have

266
00:19:46,160 --> 00:19:47,640
a place where I can rest?

267
00:19:47,640 --> 00:19:49,720
Our banquet has just begun.

268
00:19:50,240 --> 00:19:51,370
Let's do it this way.

