00:33:28,270 --> 00:33:29,400
When that happens,

540
00:33:29,400 --> 00:33:30,790
with no more threats from the west,

541
00:33:30,790 --> 00:33:33,400
the Zichuan family will surely
rise to power once again.

542
00:33:33,400 --> 00:33:34,440
At that point,

543
00:33:34,680 --> 00:33:37,080
the Zichuan family
will be our real threat.

544
00:33:37,370 --> 00:33:39,300
In the current battle of Yuanzhou,

545
00:33:39,680 --> 00:33:43,010
there are also traces
of the Zichuan family's involvement.

546
00:34:34,510 --> 00:34:37,679
The more skilled people are,
the more impolite they become.

547
00:34:37,679 --> 00:34:39,679
Is knocking just not a thing for you?

548
00:35:22,480 --> 00:35:25,290
Do you think you can protect him?

549
00:35:25,400 --> 00:35:27,000
Wasn't I your target?

550
00:35:27,230 --> 00:35:28,270
Changing targets midway

551
00:35:28,270 --> 00:35:29,920
is an insult to your opponent.

552
00:35:29,920 --> 00:35:30,400
You!

553
00:36:17,430 --> 00:36:18,880
It's you.

554
00:36:49,760 --> 00:36:51,280
You're not going to kill me?

555
00:36:51,280 --> 00:36:54,110
It seems you know nothing
about your own bloodline.

556
00:36:54,110 --> 00:36:55,440
I don't have to kill you.

557
00:36:55,840 --> 00:36:56,840
One day,

558
00:36:57,000 --> 00:36:59,360
the Sacred Land will give you the answer.

559
00:37:24,480 --> 00:37:25,410
Are you alright?

560
00:37:26,280 --> 00:37:28,070
Your eyes turned red just now.

561
00:37:29,030 --> 00:37:30,920
His eyes turned red just now.

562
00:37:30,920 --> 00:37:32,120
You must be mistaken.

563
00:37:33,150 --> 00:37:34,010
Come back here.

564
00:37:34,320 --> 00:37:36,580
Don't you know your own eyes can turn red?

565
00:37:36,920 --> 00:37:39,720
Do you expect me to look in a mirror
while fighting?

566
00:37:41,000 --> 00:37:43,400
Zichuan Xiu, who on earth are you?

567
00:37:43,670 --> 00:37:45,230
I am the King of Light.

568
00:37:45,600 --> 00:37:47,920
You're definitely more than
just the King of Light.

569
00:37:47,920 --> 00:37:50,320
Does it matter who I am?

570
00:37:50,690 --> 00:37:51,750
Doesn't it matter?

571
00:37:52,070 --> 00:37:53,070
Does it matter?

572
00:37:53,470 --> 00:37:55,930
You managed to survive
Black Veil's attack.

573
00:37:56,430 --> 00:38:01,600
And you transform
during fights just like him.

574
00:38:02,150 --> 00:38:03,350
None of that matters.

575
00:38:04,480 --> 00:38:07,800
Where is the Sacred Land
he mentioned earlier?

576
00:38:08,660 --> 00:38:10,880
The Sacred Land,
also called the Holy Ground,

577
00:38:10,880 --> 00:38:13,870
is the most mysterious place
in the entire North Clan.

578
00:38:13,870 --> 00:38:15,470
Just as the Counsellor said,

579
00:38:15,910 --> 00:38:18,600
you have a connection to the Sacred Land.

580
00:38:19,000 --> 00:38:20,300
No wonder.

581
00:38:21,150 --> 00:38:24,350
I finally don't feel ashamed about
losing to you anymore.

582
00:38:28,050 --> 00:38:28,710
What do you mean?

583
00:38:28,710 --> 00:38:30,030
Go treat your wounds.

584
00:38:31,280 --> 00:38:32,200
I'm fine.

585
00:38:33,460 --> 00:38:34,790
Transform for me again.

586
00:38:35,090 --> 00:38:35,710
Like that...

587
00:38:35,710 --> 00:38:37,440
Transform my foot! Let's go.

588
00:38:43,470 --> 00:38:44,450
Recently,

589
00:38:44,480 --> 00:38:46,700
Master's pulse has stabilized.

590
00:38:47,120 --> 00:38:49,980
Thanks to the medicine
Your Highness brought back.

591
00:38:49,980 --> 00:38:51,490
As long as he takes good care of himself,

592
00:38:51,490 --> 00:38:54,080
I'm sure the Master will recover soon.

593
00:38:54,100 --> 00:38:56,430
Glad to hear that.

594
00:39:01,990 --> 00:39:05,050
It's great that the medicine
I brought back is working.

595
00:39:05,260 --> 00:39:06,120
But, Father...

596
00:39:06,440 --> 00:39:08,140
Zichuan must have already learned

597
00:39:08,140 --> 00:39:09,740
about your serious illness.

598
00:39:10,020 --> 00:39:11,680
I need to go and guard Lan City.

599
00:39:12,430 --> 00:39:15,230
Now that your health
has improved significantly,

600
00:39:16,220 --> 00:39:17,750
I must depart immediately.

601
00:39:22,800 --> 00:39:25,660
Shuang, I'm sorry for the hardship
you must endure.

602
00:39:26,840 --> 00:39:30,630
I've heard that Yuanzhou
now has a King of Light.

603
00:39:31,000 --> 00:39:32,520
In just one year,

604
00:39:32,540 --> 00:39:34,070
he has led Yuanzhou to rise.

605
00:39:34,190 --> 00:39:36,500
His strength is not to be underestimated.

606
00:39:36,500 --> 00:39:39,170
The Xichuan Continent
is not what it used to be.

607
00:39:39,320 --> 00:39:40,720
Canxing is incompetent.

608
00:39:41,110 --> 00:39:43,590
Though he seized power from Yang Minghua,

609
00:39:44,030 --> 00:39:46,960
he lacks the ability
to make Zichuan powerful again.

610
00:39:48,440 --> 00:39:51,190
Zichuan controls the largest territory

611
00:39:51,510 --> 00:39:53,040
and the richest resources.

612
00:39:53,440 --> 00:39:56,940
Yet his clan can only watch
as their century-old legacy

613
00:39:57,210 --> 00:39:58,770
gradually

614
00:39:58,800 --> 00:40:01,530
slips away from their noble name.

615
00:40:02,230 --> 00:40:04,760
Now, the key question is

616
00:40:05,280 --> 00:40:07,280
who will ultimately seize Zichuan.

617
00:40:07,360 --> 00:40:09,690
Is there no hope
for Zichuan to rise again?

618
00:40:10,510 --> 00:40:11,910
Absolutely impossible.

619
00:40:13,120 --> 00:40:14,340
The power of the Divine Emperor of Sairong

620
00:40:14,340 --> 00:40:16,200
surpasses all our expectations.

621
00:40:16,540 --> 00:40:19,870
It is a pity that among
the next generation of Sairong heirs,

622
00:40:20,010 --> 00:40:21,960
none carry the true presence of a ruler.

623
00:40:21,960 --> 00:40:24,030
The Lin family has always
kept to themselves

624
00:40:24,030 --> 00:40:26,690
and won't interfere in
continental conquests.

625
00:40:27,000 --> 00:40:30,480
Moreover, we've been on good terms
with the Lin family for generations.

626
00:40:30,480 --> 00:40:31,760
So, Shuang,

627
00:40:32,360 --> 00:40:34,820
the rise and future
of the Xichuan Continent

628
00:40:34,840 --> 00:40:38,920
lies with you and the King of Light.

629
00:40:47,400 --> 00:40:48,660
Including yesterday,

630
00:40:48,690 --> 00:40:50,420
you've saved me several times.

631
00:40:50,650 --> 00:40:51,560
I've made up my mind.

632
00:40:51,560 --> 00:40:52,850
I accept your offer.

633
00:40:56,020 --> 00:40:58,230
I, Lu Di, pledged my loyalty to you,
the King of Light,

634
00:40:58,230 --> 00:41:01,360
swearing to follow you
and defend Yuanzhou with my life.

635
00:41:02,400 --> 00:41:06,070
Good, very good.

636
00:41:11,810 --> 00:41:15,070
These are letters written to you
by representatives of various races.

637
00:41:15,070 --> 00:41:15,920
So many?

638
00:41:22,720 --> 00:41:25,930
This letter is from
the Snake Race delegation.

639
00:41:26,810 --> 00:41:28,730
If we recruit Lu Di,

640
00:41:28,900 --> 00:41:31,660
they'll withdraw their beauty envoys.

641
00:41:32,960 --> 00:41:34,000
What?

642
00:41:35,840 --> 00:41:37,560
If we recruit Lu Di,

643
00:41:37,580 --> 00:41:40,420
they'll just pull their troops back
and go mining.

644
00:41:41,590 --> 00:41:43,850
This is from the Dragon Race delegation.

645
00:41:45,590 --> 00:41:48,000
My Lord, recruiting him

646
00:41:48,000 --> 00:41:50,090
would only ignite anger
throughout Yuanzhou.

647
00:41:50,090 --> 00:41:52,690
It's not worth it,
and it's not like your style.

648
00:41:52,940 --> 00:41:55,900
Actually, whether it's the Zichuan family,

649
00:41:56,530 --> 00:41:59,610
the Snake Race, the Dragon Race,
or even the North Clan,

650
00:42:00,440 --> 00:42:02,570
why can't we set aside our prejudices

651
00:42:03,770 --> 00:42:06,540
and live in harmony?

652
00:42:08,400 --> 00:42:10,760
Besides, there's something more urgent

653
00:42:11,480 --> 00:42:13,040
on my mind right now.

654
00:42:13,180 --> 00:42:15,400
Luo Si of the Data Tribe
is leading a large army this way.

655
00:42:15,400 --> 00:42:17,030
You're thinking about how to deal with it?

656
00:42:17,030 --> 00:42:17,840
Yes.

657
00:42:18,770 --> 00:42:21,330
Recapturing Payi City is our top priority.

658
00:42:22,050 --> 00:42:23,450
I know Payi City well.

659
00:42:23,860 --> 00:42:25,320
It's easy to defend
but difficult to attack.

660
00:42:25,320 --> 00:42:26,970
Once Luo Si occupies it

661
00:42:27,000 --> 00:42:27,930
as a stronghold,

662
00:42:28,380 --> 00:42:31,190
it will be our greatest disaster.

